    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A reed organ on which the player maintains the air pressure needed for creating the sound in the free reeds by pumping foot pedals.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
